{"id": "qbv1665702599441", "title": "retrieve/a", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "retrieve/a"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbv1665702599441.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">retrieve/a</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: retrieve \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: retrieve \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyd1665702599286.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: retrieve/o \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: retrieve/o \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kld1665702599590.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbv1665702599441.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbv1665702599441.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbv1665702599441.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531184\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531184\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qbv1665702599441.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qbv1665702599441.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qbv1665702599441.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qbv1665702599441\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__retrieve_a_236208\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Retrieve multiple additional occurrences of the specified entity without discarding the hitlist.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__topic_d76460e1_d76461e1_d76462e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__p_d76463e1_d76464e1_d76465e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__topic_d50227e1_d50228e1_d50229e1_d50230e1_d50231e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d298934e68\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__d6294e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__d6294e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__d6294e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__d6294e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__d6294e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__d6294e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__d6294e20__entry__3\">\n Entity to be retrieved. Can be omitted in entity and field-level triggers, where there is a current entity.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__topic_d50232e1_d50233e1_d50234e1_d50235e1_d50236e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d298934e122\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1__entry__2\">\n No hits were found using the profile.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n <p class=\"p\">Since <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span> can activate read triggers, the values in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> after <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span> might have been set by the ProcScript in the read trigger. Keep this in mind when testing following a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span> statement.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7250e1_d7251e1_d7252e1__entry__2\">\n Success. Number of occurrences that match the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span> profile occurrence.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__2\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-12</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__3\">\n Errors during database I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-30</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UNETERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__3\">\n Errors during network I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qbv1665702599441__table_d7253e1_d7254e1_d7255e1__entry__3\"> The entity name provided is not a valid name\n                        or the entity is not in the component structure. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__topic_d50237e1_d50238e1_d50239e1_d50240e1_d50241e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d298934e329\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__topic_d50242e1_d50243e1_d50244e1_d50245e1_d50246e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d298934e339\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__p_d76481e1_d76482e1_d76483e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span> uses the current occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> as a profile to retrieve multiple occurrences matching that profile statement. It is an extension of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/x</span> statement.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__p_d76484e1_d76485e1_d76486e1\">When using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span> statement, you need to create a separate occurrence for the new retrieve profile.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__p_d76487e1_d76488e1_d76489e1\">Uniface searches for the occurrence in the following way:</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__li_d32870e1_d32871e1_d32872e1\">If the currently active hitlist is stepped and not yet completed, it is completed first.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__li_d32873e1_d32874e1_d32875e1\">A <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">where</span> clause is generated based on the retrieve profile (the current occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>). A database query for retrieving multiple records is executed.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__li_d32876e1_d32877e1_d32878e1\">The hits from the new hitlist returned by the DBMS are added to the existing hitlist.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__li_d32879e1_d32880e1_d32881e1\">The retrieve profile occurrence is deleted.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__li_d32882e1_d32883e1_d32884e1\">The extended hitlist is completed if it was stepped.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__li_d32885e1_d32886e1_d32887e1\">Duplicate entries from the hitlist are removed.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__li_d32888e1_d32889e1_d32890e1\">The first newly added occurrence is loaded.\n </li>\n</ol>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__section_wzn_xtl_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d298934e397\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example retrieves occurrences with a new profile using\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span> :</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qbv1665702599441__pre_jnz_xtl_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">clear\nPK = 1\nretrieve\ncreocc ; create occurrence for profile\nPK = \"&gt;10\"\nretrieve/a ; retrieve\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ebm1665702598309.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lookup</a><p>Count the number of occurrences that match the current profile.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyd1665702599286.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve</a><p>Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zqj1719931734136.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve/x</a><p>Retrieve an additional occurrence of the specified entity without discarding the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kld1665702599590.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve/o</a><p>Attempt to locate an occurrence of an entity using the current primary key value.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/emi1665702599671.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger leaveModifiedKey</a><p>Location for ProcScript that determines what happens after a key (especially a compound key) of an occurrence is modified. Applicable only in form components.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531184\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531184\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "retrieve/a Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Retrieve multiple additional occurrences of the specified entity without discarding the hitlist. retrieve/a { Entity } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity to be retrieved. Can be omitted in entity and field-level triggers, where there is a current entity. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 0 No hits were found using the profile. <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. Since retrieve/a can activate read triggers, the values in $status and $procerror after retrieve/a might have been set by the ProcScript in the read trigger. Keep this in mind when testing following a retrieve/a statement. >0 Success. Number of occurrences that match the retrieve/a profile occurrence. Table 3. Values commonly returned by $procerror following retrieve/a Value Error constant Meaning -2 through -12 <UIOSERR_*> Errors during database I/O. -16 through -30 <UNETERR_*> Errors during network I/O. -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not in the component structure. Use Allowed in all component types. Description retrieve/a uses the current occurrence of Entity as a profile to retrieve multiple occurrences matching that profile statement. It is an extension of the retrieve/x statement. When using the retrieve/a statement, you need to create a separate occurrence for the new retrieve profile. Uniface searches for the occurrence in the following way: If the currently active hitlist is stepped and not yet completed, it is completed first. A where clause is generated based on the retrieve profile (the current occurrence of Entity ). A database query for retrieving multiple records is executed. The hits from the new hitlist returned by the DBMS are added to the existing hitlist. The retrieve profile occurrence is deleted. The extended hitlist is completed if it was stepped. Duplicate entries from the hitlist are removed. The first newly added occurrence is loaded. Example: Using retrieve/a The following example retrieves occurrences with a new profile using retrieve/a : clear PK = 1 retrieve creocc ; create occurrence for profile PK = \">10\" retrieve/a ; retrieve Copy Related Links lookup Count the number of occurrences that match the current profile. retrieve Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity. retrieve/x Retrieve an additional occurrence of the specified entity without discarding the hitlist. retrieve/o Attempt to locate an occurrence of an entity using the current primary key value. trigger leaveModifiedKey Location for ProcScript that determines what happens after a key (especially a compound key) of an occurrence is modified. Applicable only in form components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}